
====================================================================================================
SELECTED SALAD RECIPES LIST (TAKEN FROM A COMPREHENSIVE LIST)
====================================================================================================

Grain Salads: 
    #1 - Sorghum Salad — toothsome sorghum with roasted peppers, beans, and bold vinaigrette.
    #2 - Wild Rice Salad — nutty wild rice with dried fruit, nuts, celery, and a citrusy dressing.
    #3 - Greek-style Grain Salad (farro or barley with cucumber, tomato, olives, feta) — classic Mediterranean flavors on a chewy grain base.

Mixed Protein Salads: 
    #4 - Niçoise Salad — composed salad with tuna (or anchovy), hard boiled egg, potatoes, green beans, olives.
    #5 - Cobb Salad — chopped greens topped with grilled chicken, bacon, hard boiled egg, avocado, tomato, blue cheese.
    #6 - Warm Steak and Shrimp Salad (surf and turf salad) — sliced grilled steak paired with seared shrimp over peppery greens and warm vinaigrette.

Fruit Salad: 
    #7 - Poached Pear Salad — pears poached in wine or spiced syrup, served chilled with nuts and cheese. - 83
    #8 - Fig and Prosciutto Salad — fresh figs, prosciutto, arugula, and a honey balsamic finish. - 46

Personal Additions: 
    9 Tabbouleh — parsley-forward Levantine salad with bulgur, tomatoes, mint, lemon and olive oil.
    10 Mediterranean Chickpea Salad (Pan Mediterranean chana salad) — chickpeas with tomato, cucumber, red onion, herbs, lemon, and olive oil.
    11 Pasta Puttanesca Salad — cooled pasta tossed with a puttanesca mix: tomatoes, olives, capers, anchovy, garlic, and parsley.
    12 Mango and Avocado Salad — sweet mango with creamy avocado, lime, cilantro, and chili flakes.
    13 Taco Salad (protein mix) — greens or shells topped with seasoned beef, shredded chicken, beans, cheese, and salsa
    14 Jellied Fruit Salad (classic retro style) — fruit set in gelatin, sometimes with marshmallows or nuts.
    15 Kisir (turkish salad)
    16 Southwestern Pasta Salad — pasta with black beans, corn, bell peppers, cilantro, avocado, and a lime chipotle or cumin vinaigrette.
    17 Corn and tomato succotash salad — fresh corn, tomatoes, peppers, herbs — summer staple.
    18 Black Bean and Corn Salad (Mexican style) — black beans, corn, peppers, cilantro, lime; versatile and staple for summer.

